Summary: The PPP daemon and documentation
License: distributable
Group: System/Servers

Url: http://ppp.samba.org

Source0: %name-%version.tar
Source2: ppp.pamd
Source4: ppp.control
Source5: ppp.logrotate
Source6: ppp.tmpfiles
Source7: 95-ppp.rules

